criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Both gender;

          -  Fitzpatrick phototypes I - IV;

          -  age between 40 and 75 years;

          -  photodamaged skin with at least 1 lesion of actinic keratosis, without previous
             treatment for at least 3 months before starting the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  photosensitivity;

          -  local or systemic infections;

          -  immunosuppression;

          -  any systemic disease that could contraindicate the procedure.
